quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,28,"Ne olwa witsa okhunyoola obwihotselefu ewe nende abali halala ninawe mubwaro obo, boola mbu; “Okhwitsomibwa khwoosi nikhwa Nyasaye owakhuhabina efwe okhurulana nende Abandu ababii.”"
  23,29,"Ne boola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje, nzishia habundu wetsimbabaasi, ne toto ewe newe omulayi muno wokhwishia.”"
  23,30,"Toto mukano kalimwo ameeko amakhongo, ne toto efwe khwali bokhubakholela amatemo."
  23,31,"Mana nikhurera inyuma wabu Abandu bandi."
  23,32,"Mana nikhubarumila Abarumwa okhurula mubo okhubaboolela mbu; “Laame Nyasaye, mubula nyasaye wundi owulali Ye tawe, shimuritsangakhwo tawe?”"
  23,33,"Mana omukanda kwabakhongo babakhayi mubandu bebe okwakhaya nikuyingasia omukhung’ano kweyindukho, mana nikhubayindiasia khubulamu bwo khushialo, baboola mbu; “Uno shini shiosishiosi tawe halali ni Omundu shinga enywe, alitsanga ebia mulitsanga, ne anywetsanga ebia munywetsanga."
  23,34,"Ne nimuloonda Omundu butswa shinga enywe, mulaba musishile."
  23,35,"Koo, abalakanga mbu nimumalile okhufwa mwaba liloba nende ebikumba, mbu mulilamusibwa?"
  23,36,"Shikanyalikhana tawe, shikanyalikhana tawe, akamulakungwa ako."
  23,37,"Toto buno ni obulamu bwokhushialo, khufwitsanga nekhumenyanga, ne efwe shikhulilamusibwa tawe.""
  23,38,"Toto uno ni Omundu wachishila sa Nyasaye obubeyi, ne efwe shikhumusuubila tawe."
  23,39,"Yaboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, habina esye khulwa bayingasiyie.""
  23,40,"Naboola mbu: “Ahambi hano betsa okhwiyitsulisia.”"
  23,41,"Mana oluyoka nilubabukula khubwatoto mana nikhubakhola shinga amakokha kabengabenganga khumatsi, nibakorera ehale Abandu ababii."
  23,42,"Mana nikhurera inyuma wabu Abandu bandi."